There's an insane bad ass cop, hookers, East Indian drug dealers, there's a girl dressed up as a pink bunny rabbit (a furry love interest, perhaps?), chase scenes, drugs, and well - dinosaurs.

_Pterodactyl Surprise_ (qv) is a character driven comedy with a ton of that 80s magical charm that everyone loves and is centered around a chubby Ben Stiller-esque character and his good-looking oafish best friend. There's an insane bad ass cop, hookers, East Indian drug dealers, there's a girl dressed up as a pink bunny rabbit (a furry love interest, perhaps?), chase scenes, drugs, and well - dinosaurs.::Chris

Chris and Mike are cashiers at the local 98 cent store. In order to handle the daily stresses of working in retail the guys calls Hareesh, their neighborhood pot dealer. Hareesh warns the guys that this new strain of marijuana comes with a warning... the guys throw caution to the wind, get high, and wake up in the Mesozoic Era. They end up running for their lives from an angry T-REX with a local bike cop, a cute girl in a bunny costume, and a hooker.::C
